OL,3,CHeadteacher welcomes Ofsted scrapping
OL,4,Cone-word grade as it's 'very stressful'
OL,6,FThe headteacher of an Oxford primary
OL,7,Fschool is welcoming the decision to
OL,8,Fscrap single-word headline Ofsted
OL,9,Fjudgements for schools.
OL,11,FLynn Knapp, Headteacher at Windmill
OL,12,FPrimary School has described the
OL,13,FOfsted process as "very stressful".
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, she said:
OL,16,F"It's always in the back of your mind
OL,17,Fthe fear of losing that outstanding
OL,18,Fbecause I know that's what parents see.
