OL,3,CHeadteacher welcomes Ofsted scrapping
OL,4,Cone-word grade as it's 'very stressful'
OL,6,F"The whole process of Ofsted is very
OL,7,Fstressful because the impact of a
OL,8,Fnegative judgement can have huge
OL,9,Fimpact on your school numbers which
OL,10,Fbrings budget constraints and that
OL,11,Fwhole feeling that the community feel
OL,12,Fabout that school."
OL,14,FThe announcement to scrap one-word
OL,15,Fjudgements follows engagement with the
OL,16,Fteaching sector and the family of
OL,17,Fheadteacher Ruth Perry, after a
OL,18,Fcoroner's inquest found the Ofsted
OL,19,Finspection process had likely
OL,20,Fcontributed to her death.
