OL,3,CHeadteacher welcomes Ofsted scrapping
OL,4,Cone-word grade as it's 'very stressful'
OL,6,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,7,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,8,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,9,Fhighest rating, "outstanding", to its
OL,10,Flowest rating, "inadequate", over
OL,11,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,13,FMrs Knapp says the move was needed to
OL,14,Fmake sure what happened with Ruth
OL,15,FPerry - never happens again. "School
OL,16,Fdevelopment is always ongoing," she
OL,17,Fadded.
