OL,3,CHeadteacher welcomes Ofsted scrapping
OL,4,Cone-word grade as it's 'very stressful'
OL,6,F"We don't never stand still, a good
OL,7,Fand outstanding school should never be
OL,8,Fstatic and think, 'right, that's it,
OL,9,Fwe've done it, tick the box, we've got
OL,10,Fthat judgement.'
OL,12,F"It should always be about getting
OL,13,Fbetter, and if you've got a team of
OL,14,Fpeople, you can come into your school
OL,15,Fand say, 'actually, this is great, but
OL,16,Fdo you know what, this would be even
OL,17,Fbetter if you were to do this.'
