OL,3,CHeadteacher welcomes Ofsted scrapping
OL,4,Cone-word grade as it's 'very stressful'
OL,6,F"That has to be a much more
OL,7,Fconstructive way of dealing with
OL,8,Foutcomes of Ofsted inspections, and
OL,9,Fmaking people feel that what they're
OL,10,Fdoing has been recognised and felt to
OL,11,Fbe good.
OL,13,F"We all want the feedback. The whole
OL,14,Fidea of having an external judgement
OL,15,Fis really positive for us, but it
OL,16,Fneeds to be handled in the right way."
